i  a redress of grievances.		gopher.black	70
i		gopher.black	70
iCongress is limited in their powers by the Constitution from		gopher.black	70
iabridging the freedom of speech.		gopher.black	70
i		gopher.black	70
iDone, right? libertarians have at it. Except, no. Oliver Wendell		gopher.black	70
iHolmes comes knocking next...		gopher.black	70
