iis given the power to determine what it protects from itself.		gopher.black	70
iThat's pretty weird when you word it like that, but so be it.		gopher.black	70
iWhat stands out though is that the justification for NOT		gopher.black	70
iprotecting speech is required based on the wording of the		gopher.black	70
iconstitution. The US government, at least, needs to justify a		gopher.black	70
idecision to step in and persecute a speaker (at least to itself).		gopher.black	70
